      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-16" id="multicall">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
      <code class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 rounded-lg font-mono text-lg">aura multicall</code>
    </div>
    <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Execute multiple smart contract <strong>view/pure</strong> function calls in a single RPC request using the Multicall3 standard (0xcA11...). Dramatically reduces latency for multi-data queries.
    </p>
    <div class="terminal mb-6">
      <div class="p-4 font-mono text-sm space-y-1">
        <div><span class="text-purple-400">❯</span> <span class="text-green-400">aura multicall</span></div>
